parameters: I should have refused Souta's request at some point.
In the end, the request escalated...
I couldn't help but give in...
\N<Hinata Aki> What's wrong? You seem restless.

\N<Hinata Aki> Did something good happen? Tell me, big
sister~!
\N<Muddy child> ......I've found a boy I like~!
<Hinata Aki> Who?... Do I know this person?

\N<Sota> Aki-neechan, can you listen to my request today
too?
\N<Happy-looking child> Swings are definitely the most fun!

\N<Sota's friend> I found a stag beetle earlier! Isn't it
cool!
\N<Calm child> Big brother, you seem unlucky.

\N<Muddy child> I'm going to work hard and be able to do a
reverse somersault!
